summary: An Ordinance accepting a deed from N. H. Latimer and Margaret Latimer, his wife, of Seattle, Washington, to the City of Seattle, dated the 14th day of January, 1903, to Lot Thirteen (13), Fourteen (14), Sixteen (16), Seventeen (17), Eighteen (18) and Nineteen (19) of Block "E" of Phinney's Addition to the City of Seattle.
